questions.question:
What will be the result of the following reducer after dispatching `{ type: 'ADD', payload: 5 }` with initial state 10?

```js
function reducer(state, action) {
  switch (action.type) {
    case 'ADD':
      return state + action.payload;
    default:
      return state;
  }
}
```

What will be the new state after dispatching `{ type: 'TOGGLE' }` with the following reducer and initial state `{ visible: false }`?

```js
function reducer(state, action) {
  switch (action.type) {
    case 'TOGGLE':
      return { visible: !state.visible };
    default:
      return state;
  }
}
```
